high_descs: Turn and go to the sidetable.
Open the refrigerator door. Place the apple on the second level. Close the door. Close for twelve seconds. Open the doors. Take out the apple. Close the door.
Open the microwave. Put the apple in the microwave. Close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Find an apple, cool it. Place it in a microwave oven.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the side table near the window
Pick up the apple on the side table
Turn right and head towards the counter, then go to the fridge on your left
Put the apple into the fridge, cool it, get the apple out of the fridge
Turn right and go to the microwave on the counter
Put an apple into the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled apple in the microwave

high_descs: Turn left and turn right to the side table.
Pick the apple from the side table.
Walk towards and turn left to the fridge.
Place the apple inside the fridge.
Pick it out of the fridge and turn left to the microwave.
Put the apple inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To put the apple inside the microwave.
